hadiths[18]{hadithnumber,text}:
2844,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney kutta paala , siwaye uskey ke wo janwaron ki hifazat ke liye ho, ya shikar ke liye , ya kheti ke liye to aisey shakhs ke ajr mein se her roz eik qeeraat kam hota rahega.''"
2845,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar ye baat na hoti ke kuttey bhi (Allah ki makhluq aur) ummaton mein se eik ummat hain, to main inke qatl kerney ka hukm dey deta , (beharhal) in mein se jo kaalaa siyah ho, usey maar dala karo.''"
2846,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (ibtidaai (shuruati) dinon mein) kutton ko qatl kerney ka hukm diya tha yahan tak ke agar koi aurat dehat se aati aur uskey sath kutta hota to ham usey bhi qatl kar daltey they, iskey baad aapney hamen is se mana kar diya aur farmaya : ''sirf kaley kutton ko maaro.''"
2847,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kiya ke main apney sadhaaey huey kuttey chhodta hun to wo merey liye shikar pakad rakhtey hain, to kya main (usey) kha lun? aapney farmaya : ''jab tum sadhaaey huey kuttey chhodo aur Allah ka naam lo, to jo wo tumharey liye pakad rakhen usey kha lo.''  maine kaha : agar-che wo usey maar hi dalen? aapney farmaya : ''khuwah maar hi dalen, ba-sharte-ke koi aur kutta un mein shamil na ho gaya ho jo un mein se na ho.'' maine kaha : main bhaala phainktaa hun aur us se shikar karta hun, to kya (isey) kha liya karun? aapney farmaya : ''jab tum bhaala phenko aur  ''(بسم الله)'' kaho aur wo shikar ko lagey aur usko phaad dey to kha saktey ho, lekin agar wo chorai ki taraf se lagey (baghair dhaar ke mehaz chot se usko maar daley ( to mat khao .''"
2848,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kiya (aur) kaha : ham in kutton ke zariey se shikar kartey hain. to aapney mujh se farmaya : ''jab tum apney sadhaaey huey kuttey chhodo aur un par ''بسم الله'' kaho to jo wo tumharey liye roke rakhen usey kha lo , chahey wo usey maar hi dalen , siwaye iskey ke kutta khud us mein se kuch kha ley , agar wo us mein se kha ley to tum mat khao . mujhey andesha hai ke usey usney apney liye pakda hoga.''"
2849,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum ne apna teer maara ho aur Allah ka naam liya ho phir apney shikar ko agley din pao lekin pani mein na pao (aisa na ho ke doob kar mara ho) aur kisi aur ke teer ka bhi us mein nishan na ho, to us shikar ko kha lo . aur jab tumharey kutton ke sath koi aur kutta mil gaya ho to mat khao , na maloom usko us kuttey ne maara ho jo tumharey kutton mein se na tha.''"
2850,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tumhara shikar pani mein doob gaya ho aur phir mar gaya ho to mat khao.''"
2851,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis kuttey ya baaz ko to ne sadhaayaa ho phir to usey chhodey aur Allah ka naam ley, to jo wo terey liye roke rakhey usey kha ley.'' maine arz kiya : chahey (chahe) wo usey qatl hi kar daley? aapney farmaya : ''jab wo usey maar daley magar us mein se usney khaya na ho to wo usney terey hi liye roke rakha hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : baaz agar kha bhi ley to koi harj nahin, lekin kutta agar khaye to makruh hai (haram hai) lekin agar khoon pi ley , to koi harj nahin."
2852,"Hazrat Sa'alba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuttey ke shikar ke baarey mein farmaya : ''jab tum apna kutta chhodo aur Allah ka naam zikr kiya ho to usey kha lo agar-che kuttey ne us se kha bhi liya ho, aur her wo chiz khao jis ko tumharey haath ne tum par lautaya ho (jisey tum ne apney haath se shikar kiya ho).''"
2853,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham mein se eik aadmi shikar ko teer maarta hai phir wo uskey peechhey do teen din phirta rehta hai, yahan tak ke usey pa leta hai aur wo mar chuka hota hai aur us mein uska teer bhi hota hai, to kya usey kha ley? aapney farmaya : ''haan , agar chahey to.'' ya aapney farmaya : ''kha ley, agar chahey to.''"
2854,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bhaale se shikar ke baarey mein puchha to aapney farmaya : ''agar wo dhaar ki taraf se laga ho to kha lo aur agar motaai ki taraf se laga ho to mat khao, bila-shuba wo chot zada hoga.'' maine arz kiya : main apna kutta chhodta hun. aapney farmaya : ''jab tum ne Allah ka naam liya ho to kha lo warna mat khao, aur agar kuttey ne us mein se kuchh khaya ho to bhi mat khao , wo usney apney liye pakda hai.'' arz kiya ke main apna kutta chhodta hun aur phir shikar par eik aur kutta bhi dekhta hun? aapney farmaya : ''mat khao, kyonkey tum ne to apney kuttey par Allah ka naam liya hai.''"
2855,Hazrat Abu Sa'alba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main apney sadhaaey huey kuttey ke sath shikar karta hun aur aisey kuttey ke sath bhi jo sadhaayaa hua nahin hota . aapney farmaya : ''jo shikar tum apney sadhaaey huey kuttey se karo tu Allah ka naam lo aur khao . aur jo baghair sadhaaey huey kuttey se karo to agar shikar ko zibeh kar sako to kha lo.''
2856,"Hazrat Abu Sa'alba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : ''aey Abu Sa'alba Khushni ! teri Qaus (kamaan) aur tera kutta jo tujh par lautaye wo kha ley.'' ibne-Harb ne mazeed kaha : (kutta) sadhaayaa hua ho aur tera haath jo tujh par lautaye (teer waghaira se shikar karey). to usey zibeh kar sako ya na kar sako, kha lo."
2857,"Eik badwi jis ka naam Abu Sa'alba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) tha usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! merey yahan sadhaaey huey (shikari) kuttey hain. aap mujhey unke sath shikar ke baarey mein irshad farmaiye. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar terey paas sadhaaey huey kuttey hain, to jo wo terey liye pakad rakhen usey kha ley.'' usney kaha : zibeh karkey ya baghair zibeh kiye? aapney farmaya : ''haan (dono soorton mein uska khana jayez hai).''  usney kaha : agar kutta usse kha ley to? aapney farmaya : ''khuwah kha bhi ley.'' usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey meri kamaan ke (shikar ke) baarey mein irshad farmaiye? aapney farmaya : ''teri kamaan jo tujh par lautaye usey kha ley.'' kaha : zibeh karkey ya baghair zibeh kiye. usney kaha : agar wo shikar mujh se ghayeb ho jaey? aapney farmaya : ''agar-che tujh se ghayeb hi ho jaey, lekin jab tak ke kharab na ho, ya to us mein apney siwa kisi aur ke teer ka nishan na paey.'' usney kaha : mujhey majoosiyon ke bartanon ke baarey mein irshad farmaeyn ke ham unke istimal kerney par majboor ho jaeyn to? aapney farmaya : ''unhen dho lo aur phir un mein kha lo.''"
2858,"Hazrat Abu Waqid Laisi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''janwar se jo gosht kaataa jaey, jabkey wo janwar zinda ho to wo gosht murdar (haram) hai.''"
2859,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney baadiya (jangal) ki sakoonat ikhtiyar ki, wo sakht dil hua, aur jo shikar ke peechhey pada, wo ghafil hua aur jo haakim ke paas aata jata raha, aazmaesh mein pada.''"
2860,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''jisney badshah ki sohbat ikhtiyar ki, fitney mein pada.'' aur mazeed kaha : ''jo banda kisi badshah ke jis qadr qarib hoga, Allah taala se usi qadr baeed (door) ho jaeyga.''"
2861,"Hazrat Abu Sa'alba Khushni khushni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum shikar ko (teer) maaro aur phir teen raat ke baad usey pao jabkey tumhara teer us mein ho to usey kha lo. jab tak ke boo na deney lagey.''"
